{"inkVersion":21,"root":[[{"->":"Day_One"},["done",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{"Day_One":[{"->":".^.start"},{"start":[["^\"Hello, Magetender!\"","\n","^\"It is I, the most exquisite unicorn in town, Anita Caberneigh.\"","\n",["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.4.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^\"uh.. who?\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.5.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^\"Pleased to serve you\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.4.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^\"What's that? You haven't heard of me?\"","\n","^\"Dear me, it appears I've encountered a mage who lives under a rock.\"","\n","^\"You really ought to get out more..\"","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.13.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^\"That's rude\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.13.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^\"How can I help?\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.13.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^\"Rude? You mistake my confidence for being brash, darling. You see, the former is earned.\"","\n","^\"But enough dilly-dallying, I'd like to order..\"","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.13.c-0.11.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^\"You're right, sorry\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.13.c-0.11.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^\"A please would be nice..\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c